---
// ComoFunciona.astro - How it works section with 3 step cards
---

<section class="section como-funciona reveal" id="resultados" aria-label="How it works">
  <h2 class="section-title">Three steps.<br><span class="text-verde">No fluff</span>.</h2>
  <p class="section-sub">
    Your site ready in one week.
  </p>
  <div class="steps-container">

    <div class="step reveal glass-step">
      <div class="step-number">1</div>
      <div class="step-content">
        <h3>Let's talk</h3>
        <p>You reach out and tell us your idea.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step reveal glass-step">
      <div class="step-number">2</div>
      <div class="step-content">
        <h3>Design</h3>
        <p>Results in 48 hours. We tweak. No upfront.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step reveal glass-step">
      <div class="step-number">3</div>
      <div class="step-content">
        <h3>You're live</h3>
        <p>Onboarding & free consulting.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
